task.summary: cdotc: - First implementation of the Query system, a new demand-driven architecture for the compiler. - Migrated Driver to the Query system. - Partially Migrated semantic analysis to the query system. - Started implementation of generalized extensions. - Require 'default' keyword for protocol default implementations. - Implemented support for LLVM-IR debugging.

TableGen: - Bugfixes. - Allow 'if' to conditionally define records and record fields. - Reimplemented 'foreach'. - New functions: '!eq' and '!ne' for equality checking. - Function changes: '!str_concat' takes an arbitrary number of parameters.

- added TblGen - reworked CTFE - added ASTContext - added AST PrettyPrinter and Dumper - added AST Traverse / Transform - replaced Record with RecordDecl - replaced shared_ptr's with raw pointers allocated in BumpPtrAllocator - added NamedDecl, DeclContext
- AST rework - Mixins, Static If, Static Else, improved CTFE - Parse Error Recovery - DiagnosticEngine - Driver improvements - Attribute TblGen

- exponent suffix on numeric literals - make TupleType & FunctionType use trailing objects - lldb synt providers for TupleType, FunctionType - added discardableResult attribute - added DeclarationName - added array types with inferred size
lldb synth providers for QualType & DeclarationName

- restructured IL directory layout - rewrote parts of ExprResolver::ParseExpression - typed aliases - created TypeBuilder class - fixed conformance checking and diagnostics - added 'Compiler' namespace for static reflection - lldb data formatters for ExprSequence, CompoundStmt, DeclContextUnion - fixed extensions

- restructured IL directory layout - rewrote parts of ExprResolver::ParseExpression - typed aliases - created TypeBuilder class - fixed conformance checking and diagnostics - added 'Compiler' namespace for static reflection - lldb data formatters for ExprSequence, CompoundStmt, DeclContextUnion - fixed extensions

- introduced OperatorDecls and precedence groups - restructured expression parsing - added ConformanceTable - StaticIf handling with continuation points - CTFE enhancements - added ConstantOperator IL values - added rust-like macros
- introduced Job abstraction in Driver - reworked module system - implemented async / await - reworked name lookup
- renamed CompilationUnit to CompilerInstance - reworked incremental compilation - implemented argument labels - reworked overload resolution - added compilation phase timing

- reordered declaration pipeline: protocol conformances are checked immediately after declaration, nested instantiations are not declared immediately - added clang importer for structs, functions, enums, typedefs and macros
- Fixed macro pattern compilation - added compiletime attribute - restricted function bodies that are written to modules
- removed goto - removed MemberRefExpr - implemented loop labels for 'if', 'for', 'while', 'do' and 'match'
- remove IfLetStmt and IfCaseStmt - generalized IfCondition (expression, binding or pattern) - allow multiple mixed conditions in if and while statements
- fix importing multiple source files from clang - ability to import unions from clang - ability to import complex types from clang - implemented nested pattern matching
